{
  "id": "14-1",
  "title": "Act 1: Echo of Soul",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch14_act1_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "titleCard",
          "args": {
            "text": "Chapter 14: Fragments of Memory"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Lyra didn't know how long she'd been walking.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "After leaving that place, she just started walking. No direction, no destination. Just walking because if she stopped, she didn't know if she could stand again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The Wasteland ground extended beneath her feet—rubble, dust, occasionally remnants of old civilization. She walked through these, her steps mechanical, like a shell being pushed forward by inertia alone.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her neural sync rate continued to drop without replenishment or rest. She could feel that number, but she didn't care. Caring required some level of concern for her own continued existence, and she had none.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Supplies ran out on the second day.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Water was finished on the evening of the third day.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "On the fourth day, her body began its true protests. This wasn't a signal at the neural connection level anymore—it was deeper, purely organic. Her vision began to blacken at the edges. Her steps became unsteady. She fell beside some collapsed ruins, pushed herself up from the ground, walked a few more steps, and fell again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This time she didn't try to get up.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She lay on her side on the Wasteland ground, her cheek pressed against cold dust. Her neural sync rate dropped to a critical number, flashing weakly at the edge of her vision like a light about to go out. She stared at that number for a while, then closed her eyes.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She thought maybe that was alright.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 8
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her hand hung at her side, her fingertips touching the pocket of her innermost garment. There was something solid there—a thin chain, a metal tag with worn edges. Her fingers paused at that spot, and then, maybe from some final instinct, she pulled the tag from her pocket and let it fall into her palm.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The metal was cool against her skin.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Neural Terminal ── Unidentified Signal Received ── Format Unknown",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Encryption Layer Decryption ── Key Source: Local Contact Interface ── Decryption Complete",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Timed Packet ── Timestamp: 17 Days Ago ── Unpacking",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The packet was unpacking in her neural connection. Fragments falling in—so fragmented, like a shattered mirror where each piece only reflected one corner. No complete form, no clear edges. But she recognized the texture of that data, that unique quality she'd learned over these past months, belonging to one specific person.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "It was Alea's.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 8
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her consciousness stilled at that contact.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "<whisper>Don't scatter. Don't scatter, Alea... is that you?</whisper>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1200,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}